      <title>通过巴拿马丛林路线迁移到美国99％</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-10/migration-to-the-us-through-panama-jungle-route-plunges-99</link>
      <description><![CDATA[上个月，试图通过丛林徒步前往中美洲的移民数量猛增了99％，有可能改善巴拿马与美国总统唐纳德·特朗普之间的紧张关系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-10/migration-to-the-us-through-panama-jungle-route-plunges-99</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 10 Mar 2025 15:24:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>奥班威胁匈牙利投票前驱逐双重公民</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-10/orban-threatens-dual-citizens-with-expulsion-before-hungary-vote</link>
      <description><![CDATA[匈牙利总理维克多·奥尔班（Viktor Orban）以双重公民身份为目标，这是明年大选前的宽广镇压一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-10/orban-threatens-dual-citizens-with-expulsion-before-hungary-vote</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 10 Mar 2025 15:17:57 GMT</pubDate>
